          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Is Aurelle suitable for sensitive skin?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes. Our formula uses encapsulated retinol and carefully balanced actives chosen to minimise irritation. We recommend doing a patch test before first use, as individual responses vary.</p>"
